TITLE: Embedding KyberSwap Widget in React
DESCRIPTION: Example of how to import and use the KyberSwap Widget component in a React application. It demonstrates basic configuration options including setting a client ID, theme, token list, and enabling specific features.
SOURCE: https://github.com/kybernetwork/kyberswap-documentation.git/blob/main/kyberswap-solutions/kyberswap-widget/developer-guides/integrating-the-kyberswap-widget.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
