TITLE: Executing Swap Transaction with Ethers.js
DESCRIPTION: Submits the encoded swap transaction to the blockchain using ethers.js. The transaction includes the encoded swap data, sender and recipient addresses, and gas parameters to ensure proper execution on the network.
SOURCE: https://github.com/kybernetwork/kyberswap-documentation.git/blob/main/kyberswap-solutions/kyberswap-aggregator/developer-guides/execute-a-swap-with-the-aggregator-api.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

