TITLE: Formatting Create Order Request for KyberSwap API
DESCRIPTION: Formats the request body for the create order API call by combining the unsigned order request body with the signature and salt.
SOURCE: https://github.com/kybernetwork/kyberswap-documentation.git/blob/main/kyberswap-solutions/limit-order/developer-guides/create-limit-order.md#2025-04-21_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const requestBody: CreateOrderSignedBody = {
    ...unsignedOrderReqBody,
    salt: unsignedOrderReturnData.message.salt,
    signature: signature
};
```

