TITLE: Formatting Cancel Order Request in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to format the request body for cancelling batch orders. It creates an object with an array of order IDs to be cancelled.
SOURCE: https://github.com/kybernetwork/kyberswap-documentation.git/blob/main/kyberswap-solutions/limit-order/developer-guides/hard-cancel.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
