TITLE: Querying Zap-In Route with cURL in Bash
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to make a GET request to the zap-in route endpoint using cURL in Bash. It includes the necessary headers and query parameters for the API call.
SOURCE: https://github.com/kybernetwork/kyberswap-documentation.git/blob/main/kyberswap-solutions/kyberswap-zap-as-a-service/kyberswap-zap-as-a-service-zaas-api/zaas-http-api.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
