SOURCE: https://github.com/kybernetwork/kyberswap-documentation.git/blob/main/kyberswap-solutions/kyberswap-zap-as-a-service/kyberswap-zap-as-a-service-zaas-api/zaas-http-api.md#2025-04-21_snippet_3

